reviewText: This is a must see movie!!! It should be discussed in every church across America.
Beautiful faith-based film I really enjoyed watching this, very well put together. I could watch this film over and over again.

This is such a powerful film with many life lessons for youth to adults. Women whom are in search of a life partner in marriage
Will find sound Christian methods to doing it Gods way!!
Derrick

This is a must-see film! Open discussion on the subject-matter is very much needed today. I recommend watching with your family and talking about self-respect and see if everyone's definition is on par with the family expectations.
